Beste Oranjes,

ik heb hetzelfte fout met de Nederlandse kaart gehad. Wat je moet doen, om die te lossen, is de register eendrag voor het kaartje te veranderen. En dat gaat zo:

1. open the faulty registry file in the text editor
2. delete everything
3. copy and paste the code below
4. save the file
5. now run the registry file

Enjoy! Groetjes

----> copy from here:
Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Garmin\MapSource\Families\FAMILY_802]
"ID"=hex:22,03
"MDR"="C:\\GARMIN\\FAMILY_802\\MDRMAP.IMG"
"IDX"="C:\\GARMIN\\FAMILY_802\\product.mdx"

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Garmin\MapSource\Families\FAMILY_802\1]
"Bmap"="C:\\GARMIN\\FAMILY_802\\basemap.img"
"Tdb"="C:\\GARMIN\\FAMILY_802\\product.tdb"
"Loc"="C:\\GARMIN\\FAMILY_802"

instructions for belgium dutch topo map :
make a folder "FAM_620" in the garmin folder (probably on your C drive). copy the contents of Belgium_TOPO in to that new folder. also copy Belgium_topo.REG to that folder and execute it. Now you can use the map.
